there's anyone that might be
interested in my work or...

05:33.016 --> 05:35.033
Keke introduce me to a guy,
zane.

05:36.036 --> 05:37.703
He's always sweating me
to post more.

05:39.689 --> 05:43.024
I'll be honest with you,
he's a little slippery.

05:43.043 --> 05:44.159
If you can handle it.

05:45.879 --> 05:46.995
Okay.

05:47.030 --> 05:48.113
Yeah. Thank you.

05:48.148 --> 05:49.464
-No problem.
-Thanks.

05:54.638 --> 05:55.754
Thank you.

05:55.806 --> 05:57.756
You need anything else?

05:57.808 --> 05:59.007
I'm good, son.

05:59.042 --> 06:01.259
Full as a tick.

06:01.311 --> 06:05.213
So, I hear you finally
asked sandy out on a date.

06:05.232 --> 06:06.848
I see you playa.

06:08.885 --> 06:10.102
Yeah.

06:10.154 --> 06:12.654
