to just any place.

06:24.251 --> 06:25.900
What? Give me something
to work with.

06:25.919 --> 06:28.120
What does she like?
Where does she want to go?

06:28.172 --> 06:30.622
Well, she talks
about jamaica a lot.

06:30.674 --> 06:33.058
Well, there it is.
Jamaica it is.

06:33.093 --> 06:34.843
I can't afford
a trip to jamaica.

06:34.878 --> 06:36.845
But you can afford
a real spot.

06:36.880 --> 06:39.581
So, let's say we make that
into a jamaican paradise,

06:39.600 --> 06:41.800
palm trees, reggae music,
that vibe,

06:41.852 --> 06:44.352
make some jerk chicken
and rum cake.

06:44.388 --> 06:45.637
We're gonna
make that first date

06:45.689 --> 06:47.105
with sandy a night
to remember.

06:49.426 --> 06:51.759
Okay, jamaica in st. Joe.

06:51.779 --> 06:53.528
-I like it.
-Uh-huh.

06:53.564 --> 06:55.530
Rotating our crops lately.

06:55.566 --> 06:57.566
Practicing the george
washington carver method.

06:57.601 --> 06:59.434
Yeah, our soil nutrients
have doubled.

06:59.453 --> 07:02.237
Have y'all
considered aeroponics
in the greenhouse?

07:02.272 --> 07:04.406
It uses less water,
mostly air.

07:06.276 --> 07:08.493
Fifty years, never had
no problems with air.

07:08.545 --> 07:10.111
-[laughing]
-yeah.

07:10.130 --> 07:12.164
Well, it's the same concept
as the carver method,

07:12.216 --> 07:14.166
you just need the right amount
of nutrients.

07:14.218 --> 07:15.550
After we set up aeroponics,

07:15.586 --> 07:17.385
we doubled our yield
in one year.

07:17.421 --> 07:19.421
Wow. That's good.

07:19.456 --> 07:21.223
I have something
for y'all actually.

07:22.643 --> 07:23.809
Seeds from my land.

07:24.961 --> 07:26.428
From my mother's people.

07:26.463 --> 07:30.232
Plant them, save the seeds
so you can pass them
to the next generation.

07:30.267 --> 07:32.934
I hope they bring you luck for
the council meeting tomorrow.

07:32.969 --> 07:34.135
You've come a long way.

07:34.154 --> 07:35.937
Ain't happen overnight.

07:35.972 --> 07:37.072
Takes a village.

07:37.107 --> 07:39.140
Well, it's one
of the perks of a co-op.

07:39.159 --> 07:40.308
-Community, yeah?
-Right.

07:40.327 --> 07:43.411
