that star treatment too.

07:47.167 --> 07:48.783
Encourage folks
to get back to the land.

07:48.818 --> 07:50.869
-Heard that.
-How about we talk over lunch?

07:50.921 --> 07:52.287
How about over a drink?

07:52.322 --> 07:53.588
Even better.

07:55.325 --> 07:57.825
Well, it was lovely
seeing you again.

07:57.845 --> 07:59.461
-You as well.
-Prosper.

08:02.999 --> 08:04.633
Y'all don't need anything
from me?

08:04.668 --> 08:06.017
Nah, we're good.

08:07.855 --> 08:09.354
Y'all ladies have fun.

08:11.024 --> 08:12.440
[chuckles]

08:12.476 --> 08:13.825
where are we goin'?

08:17.847 --> 08:20.932
[pop music playing]

08:22.302 --> 08:24.319
[phone rings]

08:33.797 --> 08:35.497
last time I did that,

08:35.532 --> 08:37.666
he was at a cafe across
the street

08:37.701 --> 08:39.301
and saw me ignore the call.

08:42.139 --> 08:43.555
Well, he's in chicago.

08:44.708 --> 08:45.974
Mine's in new york.

08:46.009 --> 08:47.342
So, we should be safe then.

08:47.678 --> 08:48.727
[chuckles]

08:49.980 --> 08:51.379
I love your jacket.

08:51.398 --> 08:54.048
-You look great in it.
-Thank you.

