Listen, this might be tmi,
but when I was avoiding calls,
it didn't end well.

09:00.240 --> 09:04.225
Yeah, well,
it is definitely headed
in that direction.

09:04.244 --> 09:06.227
But I still love him.

09:06.246 --> 09:08.446
He's a great guy.
Always has been.

09:08.498 --> 09:09.864
It's the reason
why I chose him.

09:12.252 --> 09:14.169
Why am I telling you
my whole life story?

09:14.204 --> 09:15.537
-[laughs]
-I'm so sorry.

09:15.572 --> 09:19.007
Look, I say just rip off
the band-aid.

09:19.042 --> 09:21.209
It'll hurt at first,
then it'll get better.

09:22.379 --> 09:24.912
Yeah.
I'm just not sure
if I'm ready yet.

09:24.932 --> 09:26.214
You don't know until you try.

09:28.719 --> 09:30.135
Call him.

09:30.187 --> 09:31.353
Hi. I'm billie denton.

09:32.922 --> 09:34.889
My mother calls me
my emani.

09:34.924 --> 09:36.758
That's a beautiful name.

09:36.777 --> 09:38.360
It's really nice to meet you,
emani.

09:38.395 --> 09:40.145
Great meeting you too, billie.

09:40.197 --> 09:41.563
Make the call.

09:41.598 --> 09:43.114
I'm thinking. I'm thinking.

09:45.369 --> 09:47.869
[phone rings]

09:54.895 --> 09:57.795
yeah, this is my idea
of montego bay
vibes right here.

09:57.814 --> 09:59.347
